ng environment that fosters active listening, encourages creativity and cultivates high quality achievement at all levels of our firm. From our most experienced consultants to the newest members of our team, we expect our people to make a difference for our clients and we give them the opportunity to do so.\r\nAllow us the opportunity to work with you.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"moffitt-body-button\" style=\"color: #445faa;\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/moffitt/?page_id=256\">Meet the Moffitt team</a>','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2019-01-16 13:11:50','2019-01-16 13:11:50','',7,'http://localhost:8888/moffitt/?p=454',0,'revision','',0),(455,1,'2019-01-18 15:34:38','2019-01-18 15:34:38','','charles-williams-v5-color','','inherit','closed','closed','','charles-williams-v5-color','','','2019-01-18 15:34:38','2019-01-18 15:34:38','',337,'http://localhost:8888/moffitt/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/charles-williams-v5-color.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(456,1,'2019-01-18 15:36:36','2019-01-18 15:36:36','','Charles Williams','','inherit','closed','closed','','337-revision-v1','','','2019-01-18 15:36:36','2019-01-18 15:36:36','',337,'http://localhost:8888/moffitt/?p=456',0,'revision','',0),(457,1,'2019-01-18 15:37:51','2019-01-18 15:37:51','','tim-moffitt-v5-color','','inherit','closed','closed','','tim-moffitt-v5-color','','','2019-01-18 15:37:51','2019-01-18 15:37:51','',330,'http://localhost:8888/moffitt/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/tim-moffitt-v5-color.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(458,1,'2019-01-18 15:40:17','2019-01-18 15:40:17','','Tim Moffitt','','inherit','closed','closed','','330-revision-v1','','','2019-01-18 15:40:17','2019-01-18 15:40:17','',330,'http://localhost:8888/moffitt/?p=458',0,'revision','',0),(459,1,'2019-01-18 15:49:37','2019-01-18 15:49:37','','Gary Pipta','','inherit','closed','closed','','327-revision-v1','','','2019-01-18 15:49:37','2019-01-18 15:49:37','',327,'http://localhost:8888/moffitt/?p=459',0,'re